          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">T<hi rend="small-caps">O</hi> Madness, S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi> bequeaths his whole estate;</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-2" n="2">Why should we wonder? S<hi rend="small-caps">WIFT</hi> is right in that:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-3" n="3">For 'tis a rule, as all our lawyers know,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-4" n="4">Men's fortune to the next of kin should go;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-5" n="5">And 'tis as sure, unless old bards have ly'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Z66537L1-line-6" n="6">Great Wits to Madness are most near ally'd.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
